  <!-- Skyrim Dragon Priest Otar Mask -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="DragonPriestMask">
    <defName>Apparel_SkyrimMask_Otar</defName>
    <label>DragonPriest Otar Mask</label>
    <description>Mask of the Dragon Priest Otar, once a just ruler and a dedicated priest, descended into madness when dark, sinister whispers infiltrated his mind. His actions led to the downfall of Ragnvald.\n\nThis mask greatly increases the resistance to cold and heat.</description>
